Introduction

2Z is a five-member boy band under UZUROCKS Entertainment & GOGO2020. The band made their debut on January 14, 2020, with their first EP "We Tuzi:"

On June 17, 2020, GOGO2020 announced that Hyunwoong had decided to leave the band. He was later replaced with Zunon, who was revealed as their newest member on July 5.

With the recent teaser for their upcoming January 9, 2025 release, they introduced new member NUVorn. Details about him have not been disclosed yet.
